	</font>

25
00:01:53,155 --> 00:01:55,035
<font color=#00ff00>
	Den Schichtkäse hineingeben.
	</font>

26
00:01:56,435 --> 00:01:58,315
<font color=#00ff00>
	Creme fraiche.
	</font>

27
