	</font>

72
00:05:20,835 --> 00:05:22,675
<font color=#00ff00>
	Balsamico.
	</font>

73
00:05:29,555 --> 00:05:31,395
<font color=#00ff00>
	Bisschen Salz dazu.
	</font>

74
00:05:31,875 --> 00:05:33,675
<font color=#00ff00>
