	</font>

75
00:05:35,955 --> 00:05:37,795
<font color=#00ff00>
	Vermengen.
	</font>

76
00:05:39,515 --> 00:05:41,395
<font color=#ffffff>
	Ein ganz einfaches Dressing.
	</font>

77
00:05:41,995 --> 00:05:44,155
<font color=#ffffff>
